{"tid":1564630,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[P牌] [預咗沉] 願榮光歸香港 - 英詞（原汁譯版）","createTime":"2019-09-13T00:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T07:58:30.000Z","uid":320369,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3987f10c40e9d9c43503c9dc029594f668ddbfd4","tid":1564630,"uid":320369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:24:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，昨晚終於第一次聽了這個交響樂團版本：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoUIDL4SB60g&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=c202caee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oUIDL4SB60g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好能正</span></span>  QAQ DLLM<br />\n然後因為自己鍾意無聊譯下詩譯下野，玩過choir之類之類<br />\n就想說譯下英文出來～<br />\n當然，稍為literature review一下就見到DGX巴個google form裡面已經有十個以上英文版本，本應就收一收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  T___T<br />\n但是！本著對原詞既愛（一秒J出血那種）還是搵到了有再生出新譯本的空間<br />\n一）部份譯詞與旋律節奏不太合，有些位置詞語被樂句切斷；想配合樂句寫個稍微好唱點的版本～<br />\n二）部份譯詞用字不完美，可接受，有改善空間～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三）有幾篇水準甚高 (e.g. 七劍巴既高汁 &quot;Glory be to thee, Hong Kong&quot;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547782/page/1</a>）但逸出了原詞結構和意思；當然呢種情況可以話已取其意，可忘其形；但是個人都還是有少少執著表現出原本結構的威力 &gt;___&lt; 亦都是自己每次見到著迷既作品會想譯既原因<br />\n<br />\n由是就誕生了下面版本，算係希望最faithful呈現中文原詞意象既成品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Glory unto Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">For whom is the land wrought in tears</span><br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">For what do our hearts burn with rage</span><br />\n昂首 拒默沉<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Lift your heads, hush no more</span><br />\n吶喊聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Let our cries pierce forth</span><br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Liberty unto this place</span><br />\n<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">How deep is the heart wrought with fear</span><br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">And still how we stand, fast and strong</span><br />\n何解 血在流<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Though our blood be shed</span><br />\n但邁進聲 響透<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Our songs of march press on</span><br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Till we build our bright Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">As the stars subside, the night befalls</span><br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹來 號角聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">From across the mist there comes a shrill of horns</span><br />\n捍自由<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Fend our rights</span><br />\n來齊集這裡<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Together we side</span><br />\n來全力抗對<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Determined to fight</span><br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Courage and wisdom be our guide</span><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">The dawn has come, now to arms! Free Hong Kong!</span><br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Justice shall come! Revolution of our time!</span><br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Long live liberty and democracy</span><br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Glory unto Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n有人唱就冇希望架啦（除非自己出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），但發夢希望有得推到俾DGX巴團隊見到<br />\n考慮下用作英文版翻譯，不過咁大想頭咱都係諗下好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677d95126fc5f977689156d98cd6d8f72487357e","tid":1564630,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T00:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-